<hr /><span style="font-size: 14px">
<ul><li><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/DoomEdit" title="DoomEdit">DoomEdit</a>
<ul><li><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/DoomEdit#Troubleshooting" title="DoomEdit">Troubleshooting DoomEdit</a>
