</span></div>
<p>This article describes the built-in editor that comes with all <a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Doom_3_engine" title="Doom 3 engine">Doom 3 engine</a> games. Always check the editor specific page for the particular game you're editing in. The map editor can be started by typing "<a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Editor_%28console_command%29" title="Editor (console command)">editor</a>" in the <a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Console" title="Console">console</a> or as a <a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Startup_parameters" title="Startup parameters">startup parameter</a>.
</p>
