<a name="Editor_basics"></a><h2>Editor basics</h2>
<p>What follows is a series of images that show various parts of the Doom 3 engine level design software and what each feature does.
</p>
<a name="The_toolbar"></a><h3>The toolbar</h3>
<p>Most of the commands that you will require while creating a level in the editor are accessible through several ways. The two main ways are either through shortcut keys, or the integrated tool bar. What follows is an image of the tool bar along with discriptions that flow from left to right. Due to the length of the tool bar, it has been split into two sections for the purpose of this wiki. In the editor itself, the tool bar is a single row of iconic buttons, but with the handle on the far left, you can drag it out to a floating window of any size.
</p>
<a name="File_Operations"></a><h4> File Operations </h4>
<p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_open.png" class="image" title="Open"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/9/90/Toolbar_open.png" alt="Open" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_open.png" /></a>
Open an existing file within the application.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_save.png" class="image" title="Save"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/6/69/Toolbar_save.png" alt="Save" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_save.png" /></a>
Saves the current map. If this is the first time of saving, you will be prompted for a new filename to be declared.
</p>
<a name="Flip_.26_Rotate"></a><h4> Flip &amp; Rotate </h4>
<p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_x-axis_flip.png" class="image" title="x-axis Flip"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/7/79/Toolbar_x-axis_flip.png" alt="x-axis Flip" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_x-axis_flip.png" /></a>
Flip the selected Brush/Entity/Patch over the X Axis.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_x-axis_rotate.png" class="image" title="x-axis Rotate"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/8/89/Toolbar_x-axis_rotate.png" alt="x-axis Rotate" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_x-axis_rotate.png" /></a>
Rotate the selected Brush/Entity/Patch over the X Axis 90 degrees.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_y-axis_flip.png" class="image" title="y-axis Flip"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/b/bf/Toolbar_y-axis_flip.png" alt="y-axis Flip" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_y-axis_flip.png" /></a>
Flip the selected Brush/Entity/Patch over the Y Axis.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_y-axis_rotate.png" class="image" title="y-axis Rotate"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/c/c7/Toolbar_y-axis_rotate.png" alt="y-axis Rotate" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_y-axis_rotate.png" /></a>
Rotate the selected Brush/Entity/Patch over the Y Axis 90 degrees.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_z-axis_flip.png" class="image" title="z-axis Flip"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/e/e3/Toolbar_z-axis_flip.png" alt="z-axis Flip" width="24" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_z-axis_flip.png" /></a>
Flip the selected Brush/Entity/Patch over the Z Axis.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_z-axis_rotate.png" class="image" title="z-axis Rotate"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/9/92/Toolbar_z-axis_rotate.png" alt="z-axis Rotate" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_z-axis_rotate.png" /></a>
Rotate the selected Brush/Entity/Patch over the Z Axis 90 degrees.
</p>
<a name="Selection_Operations"></a><h4> Selection Operations </h4>
<p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_complete_tall.png" class="image" title="Complete Tall"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/c/c8/Toolbar_complete_tall.png" alt="Complete Tall" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_complete_tall.png" /></a>
Selects everything completely inside the current brush in your current 2D view, and deletes the brush afterwards.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_select_touching.png" class="image" title="Select Touching"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/b/b2/Toolbar_select_touching.png" alt="Select Touching" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_select_touching.png" /></a>
Selects everything touching the current brush, and does <b>not</b> delete the brush afterwards.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_select_partial_tall.png" class="image" title="Select Partial Tall"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/b/b3/Toolbar_select_partial_tall.png" alt="Select Partial Tall" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_select_partial_tall.png" /></a>
Selects everything inside (also incomplete) the current brush in your current 2D view, and deletes the brush afterwards.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_select_inside.png" class="image" title="Select Inside"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/3/3f/Toolbar_select_inside.png" alt="Select Inside" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_select_inside.png" /></a>
Selects everything completely inside the current brush in the 3D view (does respect all 3 axis), and deletes the brush afterwards.
</p>
<a name="CSG_Operations"></a><h4> CSG Operations </h4>
<p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_csg_substract.png" class="image" title="CSG Substract"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/b/b2/Toolbar_csg_substract.png" alt="CSG Substract" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_csg_substract.png" /></a>
Subtract the selected brush (only) from any touching brushes. *
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_csg_merge.png" class="image" title="CSG Merge"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/0/07/Toolbar_csg_merge.png" alt="CSG Merge" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_csg_merge.png" /></a>
Any touching, selected brushes forming a convex shape are merged into a single brush.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_hollow.png" class="image" title="Hollow"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/e/e7/Toolbar_hollow.png" alt="Hollow" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_hollow.png" /></a>
Converts a solid brush into a set of brushes forming a hollow space with its outer dimensions the size of the original brush, and a wall thickness equal to the grid size. *
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_clipper.png" class="image" title="Clipper"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/0/06/Toolbar_clipper.png" alt="Clipper" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_clipper.png" /></a>
Clipper: 2 or 3 point brush clipping tool. *
</p>
<a name="View_options"></a><h4> View options </h4>
<p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_change_views.png" class="image" title="Change Views"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/3/3b/Toolbar_change_views.png" alt="Change Views" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_change_views.png" /></a>
Cycles through the available 2D views (<a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/DoomEdit_hotkeys" title="DoomEdit hotkeys">hotkey: CTRL + TAB</a>).
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_texture_view_mode.png" class="image" title="Texture view mode"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/5/5d/Toolbar_texture_view_mode.png" alt="Texture view mode" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_texture_view_mode.png" /></a>
Selects the texture view mode for the 3D view-port.
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_cubic_clip_the_came.png" class="image" title="Cubic clip the camera view"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/c/c7/Toolbar_cubic_clip_the_came.png" alt="Cubic clip the camera view" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_cubic_clip_the_came.png" /></a>
Cubic Clipping allows the user to limit the view distance within the 3D view-port leading to improved editor performance while working on large maps.
</p>
<a name="Rotation"></a><h4> Rotation </h4>
<p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_free_rotation.png" class="image" title="Free Rotation"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/c/c9/Toolbar_free_rotation.png" alt="Free Rotation" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_free_rotation.png" /></a>
Let's you freely rotate the selected objects (each on it's own). Does not work with all entities.
</p>
<a name="Scaling"></a><h4> Scaling </h4>
<p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_center_scale.png" class="image" title="Center Scale"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/6/64/Toolbar_center_scale.png" alt="Center Scale" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_center_scale.png" /></a>
Center scaling allows you to adjust the scale of the selected brush, from it's center point, equally into all four directions. *
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_scale_x.png" class="image" title="Scale X"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/6/62/Toolbar_scale_x.png" alt="Scale X" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_scale_x.png" /></a>
When active, disallows scaling on the X axis (can be combined with Y or Z).
</p><p><a href="/web/20070729231147/http://modwiki.net/wiki/Image:Toolbar_scale_y.png" class="image" title="Scale Y"><img src="/web/20070729231147im_/http://modwiki.net/w/images/5/5c/Toolbar_scale_y.png" alt="Scale Y" width="23" height="23" longdesc="/wiki/Image:Toolbar_scale_y.png" /></a>
When active, disallows scaling on the Y axis (can be combined with X or Z).
